entries.s_10: Wow.  Where did you find that old thing?  Talk about old.  I'd be surprised if that still works.
entries.s_12: It doesn't.  Can you help me fix it?
entries.s_14: Oh no.  I'm no repair man. Oh but look.  You can probably still use this fryer basket.  It belongs to the fryer anyway.  I was just using it as a waste basket anyway.
entries.s_17: I'm a tired old man living the simple life.  Always glad to say 'Hi' to travelers.  Be careful out there.
entries.s_18: You know what?  You can go see Amyva.  She's an acquaintance of mine and used to work with fryers just like this one.  I'll put her location in your datapad.
entries.s_4: I'm a tired old man living the simple life.  How are you?
entries.s_9: I'm fine.  I found this fryer...
